data.description: Discover luxury in this remarkable, custom-built home. Featuring four spacious bedrooms, each with a private bathroom, it offers exceptional comfort. An upstairs bonus room doubles as a fifth bedroom or game room, further elevating this home's versatility. An upscale gourmet kitchen, outfitted with a Wolf 6-burner gas stove, double ovens, granite countertops, and breakfast bar. Handscraped hardwood floors radiate timeless elegance throughout, while two fire-lit living areas and a dedicated office near the main suite provides convenience. The enchanting backyard, with its lush landscaping, sizeable covered patio, and outdoor kitchen, is an entertainer's dream. Abundant storage and a 3-car garage add practicality to this stylish residence located in the desired Lubbock-Cooper ISD. Experience this home for yourself - a viewing is absolutely essential!
